{
  "original_content": "# Exercise: Document Formatting (Word/Writer)\n\nThis task guides you in creating and formatting a professional document according to the given instructions.\n\n## Task Steps\n\n1. **Open the base text:** Use the file `Tietokoneen_ajokortti_tehtäväteksti.md`.\n2. **Clean the text:** Remove unnecessary line breaks and blank lines under headings.\n3. **Basic formatting:**\n    * Font: **Arial**\n    * Size: **12 pt**\n    * Line spacing: **1.5**\n    * Alignment: **Both margins** (Justified)\n    * Hyphenation: **On**\n4. **Headings:** Replace paragraph numbers (1, 2, 3) with descriptive subheadings:\n    * **Objective**\n    * **Result**\n    * **Tool**\n5. **Indentation:** Use dependent indentation.\n    * Subheadings start from the margin (C0).\n    * Body text starts at **4.6 cm** (C2).\n6. **Headers and footers:**\n    * **Header:** Left side appropriate image (width 1/4 of page), right side fixed date.\n    * **Footer:** Left side your own name, right side page numbering in the format `page x (y)`.\n7. **Final touches:** Check with preview that paragraphs don't split across pages untidily.\n8. **Save:** Save as `Tietokoneen A-ajokortti tutkinto.rtf` or `.docx`.\n\n---\n**Addition:** Add a brief description of TIEKE qualifications (@-card, A-degree, AB-degree, TIETY) at the end of the document.",
